# Build artifacts and deps — recreated inside the image
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.vite
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output

# Secrets — never bake into images. .env.example is intentionally kept (placeholders only).
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/.env.production
**/.env.production.local
**/.keys
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.p12
**/*.pfx

# VCS and CI metadata
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes
**/.github

# Editor / OS junk
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Local-only tooling and notes
**/CLAUDE*.md
**/.claude
**/graphify-out
docs/adr

# Compose files don't belong in images
docker-compose*.yml

# Logs and tmp
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/.cache
**/*.tmp
